Group Benefits in the Package Data Model 

The Mid-Term Adjustments Lightning web component shows group members, dependents, and plan selections. It helps browse through large data sets efficiently.

Configure New Hire Enrollment and Termination Workflows for the Salesforce Data Model 
The Mid-term Adjustments Lightning web component gives insurance carrier administrators a straightforward way to terminate group census members individually or in bulk asynchronously and enroll new hires in the middle of a contract term asynchronously.

The Mid-Term Adjustments Lightning web component gives insurance carrier administrators a straightforward way to:
terminate group census members individually or in bulk asynchronously
enroll new hires in the middle of a contract term asynchronously
